{"title":"花换花","authors":["张明权"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花换花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮挂在杨柳枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳荫底下掏缏子；（注一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹二人肩靠肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄声悄语谈心思："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天上的小燕成对飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滩里的大雁配对对。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和姐夫订了婚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖了年把再不提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵班里数着他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊妹团里数着你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千人里挑来万人里拣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你两人心思到一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘自选’（注二）的亲事情意深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两家大人又同意；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想到你们订了婚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作的劲头更加足；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐夫领导互助组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歇晌的时候不休息；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你领导我们掏缏子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙得忘了把饭吃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全庄上盼着喝喜酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们几番来延迟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜瓜落蛋不去摘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们打的啥主意？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今年开展大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后就要选模范；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水流低来人走高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一个不想当状元？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年团员打先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你姐夫挑了战；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下决心带头干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单等秋天夺模范。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里选来区里选，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹吹打打送到县；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳模会上并排坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两朵红花胸上悬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿盈盈叶子随风摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红艳艳鲜花照人眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年们拿着当榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比手划脚立誓愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄酒变成交心酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆功筵变成结婚筵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县长县委来证婚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要花换花来带胸前！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注一）掏草帽缏子是平原北部普遍的妇女副业。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注二）在平原北部农村，自主婚姻叫“自选”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}